## _German cities (Part 1/4) (A-D)_

A collection of unique, handmade NFT´s from all 2055 cities in Germany. From Aach in the district of Constance to Zwönitz in the Ore Mountains. Including 20 legendary NFT´s from the largest cities in Germany. Split into four releases.



### _Collect the **[German Cities Award](https://soonaverse.com/award/0xd25aaf022279424cf6702ae5a3fd6d8b5cc0619a/participants)** to get a **discount of 50%!**_
